'''Pááfang''' is a [[Micronesian languages|Micronesian language]] of the [[Federated States of Micronesia]]. It is spoken on the [[Hall Islands]] of [[Fananu]], [[Murilo]], [[Nomwin]], and Ruo in [[Chuuk State]].
